{"tid":2230921,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗賓館疑拒交陀地費 遭掟汽油彈報復","createTime":"2020-10-05T09:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:50:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":83,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6a8fb7bcc644989f7f2c002e9efadae1917401","tid":2230921,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"元朗康景街16號，下午2時21分，二樓一間賓館疑遭兇徒掟汽油彈，兇徒逞兇後逃去，二樓梯間遺下一堆玻璃碎，地面及牆壁熏黑，現場消息指，賓館曾遭勒收陀地費，其後職員聽到爆玻璃樽聲，查看下發現梯間起火，報警求助。警員到場調查，懷疑有人掟汽油彈縱火報復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201005/77HIDXXGOVH4RM2NYBGU4UGJBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201005%2F77HIDXXGOVH4RM2NYBGU4UGJBI%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=7b3f9908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201005%2F77HIDXXGOVH4RM2NYBGU4UGJBI%2F&h=b9b21743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201005/77HIDXXGOVH4RM2NYBGU4UGJBI/</a>"},{"pid":"44d8444434128e9dd1365258878d6e0685801be6","tid":2230921,"uid":133,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"好暴力"},{"pid":"720148d21e747c6183a80acce75e079e780fa072","tid":2230921,"uid":14454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"暴徒"},{"pid":"8a23983a85faa970a6963b9f158b6ec1d7f5cee3","tid":2230921,"uid":342673,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"依間唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3381114376253feec6589f41d4b42e8a9eb8a4e","tid":2230921,"uid":132810,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀，仲陀地。<br />\n搵份正經工做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e25fdef6afb82880269139d68a4688e3693503","tid":2230921,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"rep